{"title":"黎巴嫩一小孩","authors":["袁鹰"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎巴嫩一小孩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"7月17日报载：黎巴嫩人民极端仇视美国干涉军的到来，即使是小孩子也充满了敌忾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贝鲁特街道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着一个小孩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牙齿咬紧嘴唇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛凝视港外。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上停着美国船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船上走下美国兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮靴踩上沙滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一个脚印。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩捏紧拳头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里冒出火花："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们是阿拉伯人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要赶他们回老家！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国兵踩着的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他母亲的胸脯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国坦克压着的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是阿拉伯人的幸福。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿拉伯人站起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血倾入地中海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让那沸腾的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烫死一切侵略者！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎巴嫩小孩的誓言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是全阿拉伯人的心声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这小孩背后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着全世界人民！（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔马克插图〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}